txt.en: The leader of the Woodworker's Guild has asked you to make some more spears, for it seems the fighting is not yet over.
The crafting recipes you must create can be bartered for from the Improved Recipes vendor.\n\nMake six guild-pattern spears.
The guild leader sighs.\n\n'The action in Minas Morgul has been hard, and we need to produce new weapons. It was nice to pretend we were done with war for a bit, wasn't it?'
